### Magnesium alloy SHYqp model with q=14,p=13
deg,vCoeff=yut.getCoeff('./AZ31B_Lou2007_TXT2B_SHYqp_deg14_Err_and_Coeff.txt')
maxSXY=1.0/(np.sqrt(3.0)*(1.0+vCoeff[-1]))
nQ,nP=yut.nMonoms(deg)
ddMon=yut.vPoly(deg)

## Generate data
vPoints=yut.genSpherePoints(100,moreBiax=False)
nPoints=vPoints.shape[0]
print('Number of data points = ',nPoints)
rho=yut.fSHYqp(vPoints[:,0],vPoints[:,1],vPoints[:,2],vCoeff,ddMon,nQ,nP)
vPoints[:,0]=vPoints[:,0]/rho[:]
vPoints[:,1]=vPoints[:,1]/rho[:]
vPoints[:,2]=vPoints[:,2]/rho[:]

## Extract the classical (uniaxial) r-values
Nphi=10
vone=np.ones(1)
vphi=np.linspace(0,np.pi/2,Nphi)
vcos=np.cos(vphi);vsin=np.sin(vphi)
vcos2,vsin2,vsc=vcos*vcos,vsin*vsin,vcos*vsin
##vsx,vsy,vsxy=vcos2[k],vsin2[k],vsc[k]

##tension upper part
yf,[vDX,vDY,vDXY]=yut.fGYF_SHYqp(vcos2,vsin2,vsc,vCoeff,ddMon,nQ,nP)
vRta=(2*vDXY*vsc-vDX*vsin2-vDY*vcos2)/(vDX+vDY)
##tension lower part
yf,[vDX,vDY,vDXY]=yut.fGYF_SHYqp(vcos2,vsin2,-vsc,vCoeff,ddMon,nQ,nP)
vRtb=(2*vDXY*vsc-vDX*vsin2-vDY*vcos2)/(vDX+vDY)
###compression lower part
yf,[vDX,vDY,vDXY]=yut.fGYF_SHYqp(-vcos2,-vsin2,-vsc,vCoeff,ddMon,nQ,nP)
vRcb=(2*vDXY*vsc-vDX*vsin2-vDY*vcos2)/(vDX+vDY)
###compression upper part
yf,[vDX,vDY,vDXY]=yut.fGYF_SHYqp(-vcos2,-vsin2,vsc,vCoeff,ddMon,nQ,nP)
vRca=(2*vDXY*vsc-vDX*vsin2-vDY*vcos2)/(vDX+vDY)


def pwAct10(x):
    return (x**9)*tf.math.maximum(0.0,x)

opt=keras.optimizers.RMSprop(learning_rate=0.0001)
mmval=0.975  ;mmval=0.5
nun=60
model=keras.Sequential([
layers.Dense(nun,activation=pwAct10,use_bias=False,
             #kernel_initializer=keras.initializers.RandomUniform(minval=-mmval, maxval=mmval, seed=gseed),
             #kernel_initializer=keras.initializers.GlorotUniform(gseed),
             kernel_regularizer=keras.regularizers.L2(l2=1e-6)),
layers.Dense(1,use_bias=False,
             kernel_constraint=keras.constraints.NonNeg(),
             #kernel_initializer=keras.initializers.Ones(),
             #trainable=False
             kernel_regularizer=keras.regularizers.L2(l2=1e-6),
            )
])

scl=0.0025
##augment regularizer
x=tf.Variable(tf.stack([vcos2,vsin2,vsc],axis=1))
xb=tf.Variable(tf.stack([vcos2,vsin2,-vsc],axis=1))
tf.cast(x,tf.float32);tf.cast(xb,tf.float32)
def ctreg(vw):
    freg=1e-6 * tf.reduce_sum(tf.square(vw))
    with tf.GradientTape(persistent=True) as tape:
        tape.watch(x)
        tape.watch(xb)
        yfta = model(x)
        yftb = model(xb)
        yfcb = model(-x)
        yfca = model(-xb)
    vvv=tape.gradient(yfta, x)
    vDX,vDY,vDXY = tf.cast(vvv[:,0],tf.float32),tf.cast(vvv[:,1],tf.float32),tf.cast(vvv[:,2],tf.float32)
    freg=freg+scl*tf.reduce_sum((vDXY*vsc-(vRta+vsin2)*vDX-(vRta+vcos2)*vDY)**2)
    vvv=tape.gradient(yftb, xb)
    vDX,vDY,vDXY = tf.cast(vvv[:,0],tf.float32),tf.cast(vvv[:,1],tf.float32),tf.cast(vvv[:,2],tf.float32)
    freg=freg+scl*tf.reduce_sum((vDXY*vsc-(vRtb+vsin2)*vDX-(vRtb+vcos2)*vDY)**2)
    vvv=tape.gradient(yfcb, x)
    vDX,vDY,vDXY = tf.cast(vvv[:,0],tf.float32),tf.cast(vvv[:,1],tf.float32),tf.cast(vvv[:,2],tf.float32)
    freg=freg+scl*tf.reduce_sum((vDXY*vsc-(vRcb+vsin2)*vDX-(vRcb+vcos2)*vDY)**2)
    vvv=tape.gradient(yfca, xb)
    vDX,vDY,vDXY = tf.cast(vvv[:,0],tf.float32),tf.cast(vvv[:,1],tf.float32),tf.cast(vvv[:,2],tf.float32)
    freg=freg+scl*tf.reduce_sum((vDXY*vsc-(vRca+vsin2)*vDX-(vRca+vcos2)*vDY)**2)
    del tape
    return freg

setattr(model.layers[1],'kernel_regularizer',ctreg)
with keras.utils.custom_object_scope({'ctreg': ctreg,'pwAct10':pwAct10}):
    model_json = model.to_json()
    model = keras.models.model_from_json(model_json)


if(1):
    model.load_weights(loadFile)
else:
    model.load_weights(prevW)

model.compile(optimizer=opt,loss=keras.losses.MeanSquaredError(),metrics=["accuracy"])
#keras.utils.set_random_seed(99)
np.random.seed(gseed)
random.seed(gseed)
tf.random.set_seed(gseed)
history=model.fit(
vPoints,
vTargets,
epochs=400,
batch_size=16,
#batch_size=nPoints,
validation_data=()
)
